<h2 class="styleguide__header">Tabs</h2>
<h4>Usage</h4>
<p>
	Trigger: <span class="code">data-component="tab-group"</span>	
</p>

<p>
 Tab <span class="code">href</span> is used to define the selector of the corresponding content container. In most cases this should be an id.
</p>	


